<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Tellus" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Tellus,</orth> the earth, personified: <cit><quote>Neptune's salt wash and --' orbed ground,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 166</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I will rob T. of her weed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 4.1.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 1, 14</bibl></cit>.
